{"type":null,"faqId":44185,"title":"为什么用流光快门的各种模式拍摄，最终成像是惨白一片","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">这几个模式（车水马龙/光绘涂鸦/绚丽星空模式）需要利用长曝光形成轨迹，因此对曝光时间有一个下限，在较亮的场景中会有过曝的情况，所以建议在典型场景下拍摄效果最佳。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">车水马龙的典型场景是在夜晚拍摄车灯移动的轨迹；光绘涂鸦的典型场景是在晚上无光源的场景或者在比较暗的房间内拍摄光源移动的轨迹；绚丽星轨的典型场景是在户外拍摄繁星银河或星星运动的轨迹。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"9686","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442400272000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10,CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":2,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"相机,流光快门,白天,照片全白","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}